1
00:01:57,300 --> 00:02:00,770
Our students are getting better and better

2
00:02:02,290 --> 00:02:04,300
And they all show their personal styles

3
00:02:05,900 --> 00:02:07,610
You are talking like you often come here

4
00:02:08,890 --> 00:02:14,610
More often than you think

5
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:19,450
How come I’ve never met you?

6
00:02:25,810 --> 00:02:30,400
It’s still early, you want to take a walk in campus?

7
00:02:34,900 --> 00:02:36,050
Come

8
00:03:53,740 --> 00:04:00,660
I’ve been wondering when we separate and ran, why did that security only chase after us?

9
00:04:09,870 --> 00:04:15,930
Zhang Daniao might have betrayed us and led him to us

10
00:04:18,220 --> 00:04:23,120
I though it was because you were shining everywhere

11
00:04:27,010 --> 00:04:35,130
You are not talking about that thing -You should know

12
00:04:38,910 --> 00:04:45,370
I really missed that time when we could talk and do as we wanted

13
00:04:47,950 --> 00:04:51,430
Now we’ve all became cowards

14
00:04:55,790 --> 00:05:00,310
Look, they must envy us, too

15
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:09,460
They think getting out of campus is like getting out of a besieged city

16
00:05:13,550 --> 00:05:20,600
In or out of the wall, I’ll be wherever the one I care is

17
00:05:37,620 --> 00:05:45,980
[17.If possible, let’s start over]

18
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:04,280
Lin Sen

19
00:06:06,910 --> 00:06:09,650
Soda, please

20
00:06:13,580 --> 00:06:14,730
Thank you

21
00:06:17,190 --> 00:06:20,640
What’s wrong? You look distracted

22
00:06:22,460 --> 00:06:23,990
Is it because of Yezi again?

23
00:06:26,310 --> 00:06:29,550
I want to ask you a question

24
00:06:29,820 --> 00:06:32,710
Have you lied to Zhu Xuan?

25
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:36,290
Never

26
00:06:37,980 --> 00:06:39,870
I thought it’d be easy to lie

27
00:06:41,450 --> 00:06:46,210
But it made me feel so guilty when lying to Yezi

28
00:06:47,660 --> 00:06:53,680
Why would you lie to a girl if you like her?

29
00:06:58,950 --> 00:07:03,610
I’ve been thinking about when we were young, the good times

30
00:07:03,610 --> 00:07:06,040
She’d follow me around and call me Lin Sen Gege(big brother)

31
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,490
And she’d tell me everything

32
00:07:10,460 --> 00:07:12,240
Now Lin Sen gege became Lin Sen

33
00:07:14,020 --> 00:07:22,030
There is like a paper between us, I can’t see her nor know her anymore

34
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:30,280
You’ve done good enough in these years

35
00:07:35,060 --> 00:07:36,540
I really envy you and Zhu Xuan

36
00:07:37,810 --> 00:07:42,220
You are from different worlds but you could get closer and closer

37
00:07:43,910 --> 00:07:48,140
But Yezi and I, we are being farther from each other

38
00:07:49,190 --> 00:07:52,010
I may be lucky

39
00:07:53,950 --> 00:07:59,120
For that my first love loves me back

40
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:03,020
Right, not everyone can have that

41
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:10,440
Most of us can only have bitter sweet first love

42
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:19,560
Mine was not sweet as yours so it turns out the way it is now

43
00:08:19,860 --> 00:08:25,140
15 years of first love and one-sided love may end now

44
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:41,460
Cherish what you have with Zhu Xuan -I will

45
00:08:45,110 --> 00:08:49,310
You are so lucky -What?

46
00:08:52,010 --> 00:08:53,360
Nothing

47
00:09:01,870 --> 00:09:03,620
I’m back

48
00:09:06,740 --> 00:09:11,500
Hurry up before Sen comes -I know. I can make it

49
00:09:12,290 --> 00:09:16,810
OK, come

50
00:09:22,130 --> 00:09:25,660
You must’ve taken Yezi home, so sweet of you

51
00:09:25,660 --> 00:09:27,890
It’s not like that Mom -We just met downstairs so we came up together

52
00:09:27,890 --> 00:09:35,030
Quit standing over there, come -Come in

53
00:09:39,620 --> 00:09:42,290
Two more dishes and dinner will be ready

54
00:09:42,900 --> 00:09:45,940
No need of that many dishes, auntie

55
00:09:46,210 --> 00:09:52,220
Just let her do it, she’s been preparing for long -Come help me

56
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:55,440
Sit -Hurry

57
00:10:32,710 --> 00:10:33,950
Let’s talk

58
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:40,890
Fine

59
00:10:42,930 --> 00:10:44,410
Let’s go

60
00:11:00,590 --> 00:11:02,750
Dinner is ready

61
00:11:04,680 --> 00:11:06,170
Where did they go?

62
00:11:06,460 --> 00:11:08,810
Yezi

63
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:28,440
I remember there was a children’s park when we were young

64
00:11:28,590 --> 00:11:32,850
After we eat dinner in your home you’d always sneak out to play with me

65
00:11:33,110 --> 00:11:36,310
The park was pulled down 2 years ago

66
00:11:37,430 --> 00:11:41,010
But I still used to come here alone after dinner

67
00:11:46,100 --> 00:11:51,270
We were almost the same height and I didn’t think I was younger than you

68
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:54,040
So I hated to call you Lin Sen gege

69
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:58,910
But my dad made me

70
00:12:00,130 --> 00:12:04,330
That’s you. No one can change your mind if you decide

71
00:12:05,820 --> 00:12:09,540
Though I don’t call you Lin Sen gege now

72
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:16,890
From the day I called you that, I’ve decided you are Lin Sen gege

73
00:12:17,940 --> 00:12:19,690
Which will never change

74
00:12:26,950 --> 00:12:28,770
Lin Sen gege

75
00:12:30,380 --> 00:12:35,370
A name from kid time has decided that I’d lose eventually

76
00:12:36,820 --> 00:12:38,510
Lin Sen -I know

77
00:12:40,680 --> 00:12:47,180
I’ve thought of many ways of you refusing me

78
00:12:48,380 --> 00:12:50,160
I thought I have prepared

79
00:12:56,040 --> 00:12:58,760
I know you are the one that has always been by my side in these years

80
00:12:59,890 --> 00:13:02,900
And I know how much you’ve done for me

81
00:13:05,460 --> 00:13:10,440
I thought no one would get hurt of we just keep silent

82
00:13:12,030 --> 00:13:14,670
But I didn’t know things would be the way they are now

83
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:22,880
Don’t blame yourself. We were the same

84
00:13:24,520 --> 00:13:29,250
I thought as long as I didn’t say anything, I’d still have a chance

85
00:13:30,470 --> 00:13:33,940
Then I realized that I didn’t say anything because I didn’t want to lose you

86
00:13:36,780 --> 00:13:44,360
Lin Sen, I hope we can still be like when we were kids

87
00:13:47,430 --> 00:13:49,280
I’ve thought about giving up

88
00:13:54,180 --> 00:13:58,120
Liking you has been a habit to me

89
00:13:59,300 --> 00:14:03,580
Growing this habit might just cost me one second

90
00:14:04,440 --> 00:14:08,360
But I don’t know how long it’ll take for me to give that up

91
00:14:09,830 --> 00:14:17,900
But I’ve thought it through. I’d rather cut if off me than being awkward with you

92
00:14:23,560 --> 00:14:30,380
Since I was your Lin Sen gege when we were kids, I hope I can always be your Lin Sen gege

93
00:14:32,560 --> 00:14:33,940
You mean it?

94
00:14:36,220 --> 00:14:37,790
Yes

95
00:14:40,520 --> 00:14:43,930
I’ve been liking you forever

96
00:14:45,390 --> 00:14:48,800
But what I really want is for you to have a happy life

97
00:14:55,090 --> 00:14:57,150
I couldn’t let past go

98
00:15:00,510 --> 00:15:04,830
We were so close, why couldn’t it be me?

99
00:15:09,090 --> 00:15:12,840
But life isn’t about past, but the future

100
00:15:20,800 --> 00:15:25,430
Don’t think too much. Let’ go back for dinner before auntie blames me

101
00:15:26,830 --> 00:15:32,240
I thought you didn’t fear her -Let’s keep it a secret

102
00:15:33,040 --> 00:15:37,150
It depends -Let’s go

103
00:16:21,920 --> 00:16:25,730
Miss Cheng, why did you decide to be a writer?

104
00:16:26,470 --> 00:16:34,670
In college my major was arts, but I was more attracted to reading than painting

105
00:16:34,670 --> 00:16:39,280
Then I thought that maybe I can write something myself

106
00:16:39,580 --> 00:16:44,020
So I discovered that habit in me

107
00:16:45,150 --> 00:16:48,010
Where do you usually get inspirations from?

108
00:16:48,320 --> 00:16:56,910
Mostly from life, like stories of my friends and between us

109
00:16:57,220 --> 00:17:02,240
Did you built the main character on yourself?

110
00:17:04,270 --> 00:17:05,970
Excuse me?

111
00:17:06,430 --> 00:17:10,880
Did you built the main character on yourself?

112
00:17:11,130 --> 00:17:13,380
On many people actually

113
00:17:17,630 --> 00:17:22,050
Thank you -Looking forward to working with you again

114
00:17:26,160 --> 00:17:27,360
What are you doing here?

115
00:17:29,270 --> 00:17:32,430
I told you -Have you eaten?

116
00:17:33,240 --> 00:17:35,050
I know a good place nearby

117
00:17:35,350 --> 00:17:37,860
Yezi told me you like spicy food,me too

118
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:40,540
I’m not hungry

119
00:17:42,330 --> 00:17:44,820
Where are you going? I can give you a ride

120
00:17:45,210 --> 00:17:48,000
No motorcycle please, I can take taxi

121
00:17:53,480 --> 00:17:56,110
What now? -Taking taxi with you

122
00:17:57,080 --> 00:17:58,430
No thanks

123
00:18:01,820 --> 00:18:03,570
Wu Kai

124
00:18:04,270 --> 00:18:07,310
I’ve told you, we are not suitable for each other

125
00:18:08,120 --> 00:18:10,820
You didn’t even try

126
00:18:14,590 --> 00:18:22,850
Just give me one chance, let’s try and you might change your mind

127
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:51,030
Mr.Shao, these are only part of our productions

128
00:18:51,320 --> 00:18:53,740
Do you have any advice for our studio?

129
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:59,850
I heard from Yezi that Miss Zhuxuan is direct and quick

130
00:19:00,130 --> 00:19:03,420
You present such a complete proposal in only one day

131
00:19:03,740 --> 00:19:08,410
If you are not Yezi’s partner, I’d offer you a job in my company now

132
00:19:09,570 --> 00:19:14,530
Mr Shao, we still need more experienced tips from you

133
00:19:15,230 --> 00:19:23,090
This proposal is mainly fine, about details I’ll write them down for you

134
00:19:23,390 --> 00:19:26,930
So we can further discuss -No problem

135
00:19:27,520 --> 00:19:31,320
Mr Shao, I’ll start publicity then

136
00:19:31,640 --> 00:19:38,550
OK -Thank you -You are so welcome, You can count it on us -Mr.Shao

137
00:19:39,990 --> 00:19:49,800
Mr Shao, this is my proposal, please sign here

138
00:19:57,320 --> 00:20:04,830
Zhuxuan, this is our animation producer of this program, Xiang Ze...Xiang Hui

139
00:20:05,120 --> 00:20:12,080
Don’t you know each other? -Of course we do, we went to the same college

140
00:20:12,490 --> 00:20:14,490
Right, shige(senior fellow apprentice)?

141
00:20:14,730 --> 00:20:20,580
Since you know each other, Xiang Hui, why don’t you two discuss the program over lunch?

142
00:20:20,580 --> 00:20:25,300
I have a meeting, if you’ll excuse me -Of course

143
00:20:31,930 --> 00:20:38,050
Shige, shall we? -Please

144
00:20:57,000 --> 00:21:02,770
Mr Shao asked you and Yezi to co-charge this program

145
00:21:05,330 --> 00:21:10,900
Did you come back just for business? Don’t you have any other thoughts?

146
00:21:19,430 --> 00:21:21,050
Do you want to get back with Yezi?

147
00:21:26,130 --> 00:21:35,350
This time, I... -Cut it out, just answer my question

148
00:21:39,870 --> 00:21:45,160
Silence means no to me -I didn’t mean that

149
00:21:45,840 --> 00:21:53,320
Then what did you mean? You want to get back with her, don’t you?

150
00:22:08,500 --> 00:22:15,680
After all these years, Xiang Zeyi

151
00:22:17,610 --> 00:22:21,170
I don’t know you suddenly disappeared

152
00:22:21,870 --> 00:22:24,900
I don’t want to know what exactly happen between you two

153
00:22:25,240 --> 00:22:31,910
But I know that you are back now, if you want to be back with Yezi

154
00:22:32,200 --> 00:22:40,060
You’d better figure out what she really needs right now

155
00:22:41,020 --> 00:22:47,300
Please treat her well and don’t hurt her again, I beg of you

156
00:22:50,640 --> 00:22:54,880
I hear you -Good

157
00:22:57,740 --> 00:23:05,160
Let’s call it the day now. I’ve talked out both business and personal things

158
00:23:12,040 --> 00:23:16,930
Old rules. It’s on you

159
00:23:38,190 --> 00:23:40,420
What are you looking at? -Nothing

160
00:23:47,590 --> 00:23:53,380
Zhang Daniao, what’s wrong with you? -Nothing

161
00:23:53,380 --> 00:23:58,370
There must be something -I said nothing

162
00:24:02,610 --> 00:24:09,620
What’s in your pocket? -Nothing, just play your games -Stupid

163
00:24:24,810 --> 00:24:28,600
What are you doing, Zhang Daniao?

164
00:24:28,600 --> 00:24:30,470
Liu Xinran I have something to say to you

165
00:24:43,550 --> 00:24:46,250
I am a fairy priest

166
00:24:48,680 --> 00:24:52,160
I thought I was the best healer in the alliance

167
00:24:53,180 --> 00:24:55,900
I was born to save people

168
00:24:57,240 --> 00:25:03,030
But now I’m willing to change every one of my spiritual words and prayers into my blessings

169
00:25:03,840 --> 00:25:10,520
To shine on you. Because for me, you are the star shining over Darnassus

170
00:25:11,600 --> 00:25:15,720
You direct the way home for the traveler of me

171
00:25:18,460 --> 00:25:23,400
From now on, you will be the real light behind the darkness

172
00:25:23,660 --> 00:25:29,060
From now on, you will be my strong faith like Elune, be with me forever

173
00:25:29,750 --> 00:25:37,240
From now on, all I do will not only be for the alliance but also for you

174
00:25:41,110 --> 00:25:45,580
Liu Xinran, in name of Alan, I promise to you

175
00:25:45,900 --> 00:25:49,730
From now on, every I will become we

176
00:25:51,400 --> 00:25:56,160
You will be my holy light for life, shining on my life

177
00:26:19,630 --> 00:26:21,970
Liu Xinran, will you marry me?

178
00:26:24,550 --> 00:26:25,820
Say yes

179
00:26:28,960 --> 00:26:32,810
How about it? -What?

180
00:26:33,340 --> 00:26:36,710
Who uses a paper to propose?

181
00:26:38,460 --> 00:26:40,690
I bought a ring, ring

182
00:26:45,590 --> 00:26:52,100
I made this ring on my own. It’s ugly but I hope you like it

183
00:26:52,860 --> 00:26:54,310
I can’t hear you

184
00:26:56,270 --> 00:26:58,560
Liu Xinran, will you marry me?

185
00:27:00,710 --> 00:27:03,210
Say yes

186
00:27:03,520 --> 00:27:04,940
Put it on my finger

187
00:27:28,760 --> 00:27:30,080
Honey

188
00:27:31,750 --> 00:27:37,170
Do you know you look handsome when you cook?

189
00:27:37,630 --> 00:27:41,760
I look handsome whenever I pick up a knife

190
00:27:43,520 --> 00:27:45,530
Bad guy

191
00:27:50,860 --> 00:27:56,690
Honey, why don’t we make it over since we missed the last birthday?

192
00:27:57,810 --> 00:28:03,000
You don’t need to make over anything for me, but I need to pay a huge gift back to you

193
00:28:03,330 --> 00:28:07,380
A huge gift to me? -Yes -What’s it?

194
00:28:08,810 --> 00:28:17,440
I’ve thought it through. I’ve been working and you’ve been focusing on me

195
00:28:17,690 --> 00:28:26,420
So I prepared a big surprise for you -A surprise? -Yes -Tell me, honey

196
00:28:26,730 --> 00:28:34,070
Secret. Or someone’d say I’m not romantic

197
00:28:36,000 --> 00:28:38,680
Honey

198
00:28:38,970 --> 00:28:42,770
Just tell me what that surprise is

199
00:28:44,600 --> 00:28:50,900
It is called top secret

200
00:28:52,750 --> 00:28:59,030
I don’t care, tell me now -I’m falling -Tell me

201
00:29:30,810 --> 00:29:38,800
Hello, I’ve arrived -Key it under the carpet, take it and get in. I’m not there yet

202
00:29:42,230 --> 00:29:43,880
OK, see you later

203
00:31:27,390 --> 00:31:30,270
I’ll draw one for you every day if you like it

204
00:31:31,330 --> 00:31:34,900
Then I’d have a fall box of them when I graduate

205
00:31:35,860 --> 00:31:41,200
That box would be my propose gift to you

206
00:32:09,780 --> 00:32:11,790
You like mermaid

207
00:32:12,090 --> 00:32:16,700
Let’s name our kid humaid

208
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:49,590
Why

209
00:33:54,270 --> 00:33:55,580
Why

210
00:33:59,240 --> 00:34:02,080
Why can’t you admit that I’m still in your heart?

211
00:34:10,540 --> 00:34:15,110
Why did you leave without telling anyone? Why?

212
00:34:20,640 --> 00:34:21,940
I’m sorry

213
00:34:24,890 --> 00:34:26,920
That’s not what I want to hear

214
00:34:28,710 --> 00:34:31,450
I want to know what happened in all those years

215
00:34:37,070 --> 00:34:46,410
Why did you come back? Why did you change your name? Why did you show up again in my life?

216
00:34:46,410 --> 00:34:49,050
Have you thought about my feelings? Have you?
